description: This skill is very elementary and intuitive. Just open the skill and Alexa simply asks you a question and you have to answer. It's perfect for that moments, in family or with friends, when you don't know what to do and you need a way to start laughing again. It's also perfect for you if you don't know the capitals for learning them.
name: Capitals Test
shortDescription: A nice trivia about US Capitals of the state. Enjoy doing this game with your family or with friends.
